Phobias direct comm clicks open as the comm from scourge comes in. As 
Scourge sends the coordinates, Phobia redirects the comm back to the 
computer. If the Maximals happen to stumble across his direct 
frequency it wouldn't look good. He didn't think yhey'd monitor his 
ship if he wasn't there.

"Good my backup plan has been set into motion." he thought to himself 
as the comm switched over.
